snippet.title: Embers of Mirrim Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Embers of Mirrim is a unique platforming adventure that will be available for PlayStation 4, XBox One and PC on May 23, 2017 and Nintendo Switch on December 7, 2017.

Fore more information: http://EmbersOfMirrim.com

Store Pages:
Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/embers-of-mirrim-switch
PS4: https://store.playstation.com/#!/en-us/games/embers-of-mirrim/cid=UP0190-CUSA07552_00-MIRRIMGAMEPS4000 
XBox One: https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/store/p/embers-of-mirrim/bq925zlv26lq 
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/596080
